{"tid":226471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新假期係舊文加番行山警告聲明","createTime":"2017-05-02T14:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T05:18:30.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5bdc6381afc93a82c5175fc48035ff9a72fd02","tid":226471,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.weekendhk.com/lifestyle/%E8%8F%A0%E8%98%BF%E5%B1%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%B3%BD%E8%B0%B7-%E4%B8%8B%E7%99%BD%E6%B3%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2Flifestyle%2F%25E8%258F%25A0%25E8%2598%25BF%25E5%25B1%25B1-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B3%25BD%25E8%25B0%25B7-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%2599%25BD%25E6%25B3%25A5%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=cfea40a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.weekendhk.com/lifestyle/%E8%8F%A0%E8%98%BF%E5%B1%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%B3%BD%E8%B0%B7-%E4%B8%8B%E7%99%BD%E6%B3%A5/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港都有大峽谷! 輕鬆行 菠蘿山 影靚相!<br />\n漫．遊世界\ton June 30, 2016 at 4:00 pm<br />\nMandy作為一個喜歡郊遊的野孩子，今次就介紹返有「港版大峽谷」之稱的 菠蘿山 ，由屯門出發，就可以到達屬於香港的大峽谷。影完大峽谷，更可以到下白泥睇日落，拍攝「港版天空之鏡」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2017年更新：</span>屯門「菠蘿山」路段，近年成為最易生意外的郊遊路段之一，未到夏季已有多宗登山求助個案。讀者出發前，請自行評估體力，需知道這路段絕非政府規劃的郊遊徑，沿途沒遮擋而且多碎石，要避免中暑求助收場，敬請做足準備，宜找經驗登山友同行，為人為己，新手初哥切勿輕率前往！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15af46ca5ab26f471d4780c6d00c81664cacefd0","tid":226471,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafc72d30c609de50348cebb18abea9be8f586cd","tid":226471,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"港版大峽谷　屯門菠蘿山驚變垃圾崗<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170121/bkn-20170121150006528-0121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F